BOAF contained quotes from The Birds. During Lawn Boy, Page walked all the way over and said hello to "Mike Side." Light's lyrics were changed to mention Tom Marshall, who was in attendance at the show. Weekapaug included Crosseyed quotes and a NMINML tease. During the Weekapaug jam, Trey and Mike stood face to face before turning to the front of the stage and stepping in unison with the music
